@startuml
|User|
start
:Clicks the Leave button;

|System|
:Retrieves the employee_id from the authenticated session;
:Obtains the team_id from the Team Page;
:Sends a query to verify whether the User is an active member of the selected Team;

|Database|
:Returns the query;

|System|
:Verifies the User is an active member of the selected Team;

if (Is the User an active member of the selected Team?) then (yes)
    :Sends a query to update the EmployeeTeam object with the left_at field;
else (no)

|User|
    :Informs the User they are not a member of the Team;
    stop
endif

|Database|
:Updates the EmployeeTeam object;

|System|
if (Was the EmployeeTeam object updated successfully?) then (yes)
    :Gathers Team information through queries;
else (no)
|User|

    :Informs the User an error has occurred;
    stop
endif

|Database|
:Returns the Team information;

|System|
:Renders the Team Page with updated information;

|User|
:Sees the updated Team Page;
:Informs the User they have successfully left the Team;
stop
@enduml